g alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wEGqA1Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZTIqPRb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PyxsHAK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0fXPS37.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6zbitmP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wLkhRSk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RdFIeon.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QbTNVv7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/E2G5icE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Uda0nkd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheReturnOfMadJuan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>76yrs old, dude tried to help folks</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UKKLoCD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4Hx2eNE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He watched the fattening of the US, he didn't know everything but he tried to help people fight it. He encouraged unhealthy people that they could change things and worked to give them the tools necessary. All with a smile.

Never judged, never insulted. He wasn't about vanity or pride. I'm not saying he was Mr. Rodgers but he's on the list.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UKKLoCD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TalkingSnake]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Like new:</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/E5LP0Up</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p1g0jO4.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/E5LP0Up</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HotCoffee9520]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The only ever picture taken of a Concorde at mach 2 speed</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vZuuwSe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9mE7Q3S.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>April, 1985, 50,000 feet (15240 meters) over the Irish sea. The photo itself was taken by Adrian Meredith, a prestigious British photographer, from a Panavia Tornado, a British fighter of the Royal Air Force. Meredith had to be quick and precise, because flying that high he had less than 4 mins to take the shot. The fighter couldn't keep up with the Concorde beyond that time. If you look at the horizon, the Earth's curvature begins to show. What a beauty!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vZuuwSe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SocialKeked]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Modern day America</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9tcHTMU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Evk3I26.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What a fucking Joyride</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9tcHTMU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FatSheamus]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Winner of hearts</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3P1RJyF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rowFdvS.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Do your best today as well!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3P1RJyF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheOneWhoWasLeft]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's funny cause it's true.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qetmmv5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kNBeAaT.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qetmmv5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A palate cleanser from... everything</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1QbJHon</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l1ecFKx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Just have a couple things, pet tax at the end, quick in n out dump morty</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oRTWaoW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vtcc0JH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Anyway here's unrelated Belgian techno anthem Pump Up The Jam but with a dog</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L2RuHrp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The two in question that I'm pet sitting. Oh it's so much easier with just the cat. I got a rule, drunks kids and dogs, I'll need a paycheck. Cats I'll do for a fridge raid. 

We had a big storm after I got off work late and doggo needs one walk a day so I decided better late than never. Mud patch. Cartoon banana peel sound effects. Luckily I ascribe to the go bag philosophy. I had just enough bandaids left for the scrapes. And Mr. Magoo'd it past most of it that would've ruined my clothes. Change of shirt, and 3 bandaids later... I'm ready for my late night/ early morning dinner</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1QbJHon</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GravyEducation]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ohio!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AvRKX0V</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GzaFAR0.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AvRKX0V</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>If I ruled the dumps, I’d free all the memes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/35q7rs2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9u6qmII.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1hacds8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HBbUe9L.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PzD57AV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tHEwk3U.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dM3JNeJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/y8xNmVL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/y1QlQmp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>