o;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2024/07/14/shannen-doherty-dead/74399542007/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/actMU4B</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KommSusserTod]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I can't stop thinking about it.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hur3BxV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gOkQMGI.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My stepson, age 25, has always been a problem. His main goal is to make me leave his mother. He's done it twice before, and literally admitted it. 

Last week (just barely 7 days) he came up to me and told me to take off my glasses. I kinda chuckled, and said no. He said it two more times, and both times I said "I'm not going to fight with you". 

He punched me three times in the face before I even tried to stop him. Broke my glasses on the first one, broke a tooth and knocked my glasses off my face on the second one, and broke another tooth on the third. Between the three I basically couldn't see from that eye, and obviously had a black eye. 

I'll skip the "fight" and just say: I wish I would've hit back. I'm not some badass fighter, but I did well in amateur MMA/boxing matches in high school... I could've absolutely destroyed him.

Instead, I just let him hit me. Over and over. I still have bruises a week later. I still have the two broken teeth. One of which JUST got fixed. 

Every day, for hours, I just think about how I should've fought back. Obviously he's not around me anymore, but I just have this fucking rage about it. He didn't have an easy life before me, and I know that. But it won't stop. 

Every day I imagine just NOT being the bigger man. I want to beat the fuck out of him. My wife, who I love, would be mad. But I just don't care right now. I can't let it go and I just want to beat his fucking face in. It would've been SOOOO easy. 

He's 25lbs under me, and even though I was an amateur teen 30lbs above me was literally my weight class.... Nobody else would "play" after the first round unless they had a big advantage. 

I'm just fantasizing about it, beating his face in. But I feel horrible too. It's my wife's kid. Even worse, I was starting to think of him as the "only kid I'd ever have". I miss him. I thought we were doing good....

Hello, death in usersub, welcome to the asshole.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hur3BxV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cindex1337]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>He is so happy!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0PqlrHc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a8U3yBt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0PqlrHc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mercbrit]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>connect two fish tanks with a modular expansion</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/b6c3kp4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9N9zoQO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/b6c3kp4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[24business1987]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My mom said she would give me a cookie if I made it to the Front Page (CHAOTIC MEME DUMP)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2bQg6Ro</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RvaXvyg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1. Harder</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/y5QHKGN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2. Insightful used car-buying advice that everyone should know.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/j6QoEaf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3. A kitten being lured out from under the hood of a car to be rescued</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r5cHdMq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4. "What? Why are you looking at me like that?"</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C23O0EY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5 *JUMPS AFTER IT*</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ENSnCmh.gi