lated a gravel patch. I wasn't even driving fast yet. Bike slid, my ankle underneath. I've never had a broken bone, but I was able to still walk on said foot, albeit in pain. Decided to visit the emergency room to check. To everyone's surprise, doc included, broken fibula. 1 month on my arse. 
